          <div class="sl-review-title">Saved my marriage</div>
          <div class="sl-review-meta">Verified Reader &nbsp;·&nbsp; <span class="sl-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</span></div>
          <div class="sl-review-text">My wife gave me an ultimatum. I bought this workbook and actually did the exercises. Understanding my triggers changed everything. It's hard work, but it pays off.</div>
          <div class="sl-review-helpful">👍 Helpful</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sl-review-card">
          <div class="sl-review-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <div class="sl-review-title">Highly actionable</div>
          <div class="sl-review-meta">Verified Reader &nbsp;·&nbsp; <span class="sl-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</span></div>
          <div class="sl-review-text">I love that there's not a lot of fluff. Read a concept, do the worksheet, apply it at work. My stress levels have dropped significantly.</div>
          <div class="sl-review-helpful">👍 Helpful</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sl-review-card">
          <div class="sl-review-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <div class="sl-review-title">Helps uncover the 'why'</div>
          <div class="sl-review-meta">Verified Reader &nbsp;·&nbsp; <span class="sl-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</span></div>
          <div class="sl-review-text">I thought I was just an angry guy. This book helped me realize my anger was just a mask for feeling inadequate at work. Confronting that was a game changer.</div>
          <div class="sl-review-helpful">👍 Helpful</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sl-review-card">
          <div class="sl-review-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <div class="sl-review-title">Great for fathers</div>
          <div class="sl-review-meta">Verified Reader &nbsp;·&nbsp; <span class="sl-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</span></div>
          <div class="sl-review-text">I hated the way I yelled at my kids. This workbook gave me the 'hit the brakes' techniques I needed to pause and respond like the dad I want to be.</div>
          <div class="sl-review-helpful">👍 Helpful</div>
        </div>

